基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 人文素養
 Quality of humanism
□ 公民素養
 Citizenship
□ 社會關懷
 Society caring
□ 國際視野
 Global vision
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 邏輯推理與批判思考的能力
 Logical reasoning and critical thinking ability.
□ 規劃、合作及溝通表達能力
 Planning, cooperation, and communication ability.
□ 創新與領導能力
 Creativity and leadership.
□ 以多元文化觀點對人類心性論述的能力
 Use Multi-cultural point of view to discuss human disposition.
 

